PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey.

Produced by Melisa D. Monts

 

Kate and Leisha share their latest home improvement projects, then discuss the HBO documentary, “Fake Famous,” and how social media impacts us all. 

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram ThePantsPod
